                                    <li class="li_unset">If you wish to obtain a Class A or Class B CDL, you must
                                        successfully complete driver training from
                                        FMCSA-approved training providers.</li>
                                    <li class="li_unset">Be at least 18 years old to drive intrastate (within the
                                        state).</li>
                                    <li class="li_unset">Be at least 21 years old to drive interstate (out-of-state)
