                        <h3>Federal CDL Application Requirements</h3>
                        <p class="excert">
                            To be able to apply for a CDL, you must first obtain a CLP. The CLP must be held for a
                            minimum of 14 days (minimum
                            days differ from state to state). A road skills test must be passed beforehand, as well
                            as any additional knowledge
                            or skills exams for endorsements.
                        </p>
